software-center (5.3.8) quantal; urgency=low

  [ Michael Vogt ]
  * lp:~mvo/software-center/display-price-property:
    - changes to displayed price and currency properties, for
      use by Unity
  * lp:~mvo/software-center/improve-dep8-feedback:
    - output failure logs for the dep8/ADT test runs on jenkins 
  * lp:~mvo/software-center/oem-descriptor-in-user-agent:
    - include the oem-channel descriptor in the custom user agent 
      string
  * lp:~mvo/software-center/size-calculation-via-aptdaemon:
    - moves the size calculation code outside of software-center
      into aptdaemon. This improves responsiveness and fixes the 
      issues described in bug LP: #988854
  * lp:~mvo/software-center/reoder-lobby-screen:
    - This branch reoders the lobby screen according to the spec at 
      https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SoftwareCenter#Home_screen and move
      display limits into enums.py
  * lp:~mvo/software-center/refactor-move-displaystate:
    - internal refactor, move the DisplayState class into the 
      softwarecenter.ui.gtk3.session.displaystate to make it more
      obvious to find
  
  [ Robert Roth ]
  * lp:~evfool/software-center/lp855581:
    - On checking the count of items in subcategories (in category view 
      to hide the empty ones) the supported_only flag has been disregarded
      LP: #855581

